
Changes in Repoint v1.2 (13 Jan 2021) since the previous release v1.1:

 - Add status cache to speed up Mercurial usage
 - Add SourceHut to the known remote repo providers
 - Fix failure to create library in deep/directory/path with SML/NJ on Windows

Changes in Repoint v1.1 (5 Dec 2018) since the previous release v1.0:

 - Add the .repoint.point checkpoint file and --directory option,
   enabling Repoint to be run automatically from some build systems

Changes in Repoint v1.0 (18 May 2018):

 - First tagged release of Repoint

